{"id":219200,"date":[{"year":1951,"month":3,"day":19}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"文学界","column":"","genre":"","count":"813","ytitle":"","mtitle":"给蕙丽娜，乔治…","ftitle":"","authors":["梅寄诗"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅寄诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这花园也似的学堂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曾经是培养绅士淑女的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最好的暖房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数不尽的美式配备，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涂着‘深切的友谊’"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自太平洋那边的‘友邦’!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"官僚买办多风光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洋行饭碗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掷地作金银簪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唔，你要作“人上人”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就得学洋腔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一一这才是绅士的本行。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淑女的第一课:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样打扮?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样作新娘?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(胰子要伤皮肤，洗脸最好用冷霜。)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第二课:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华尔兹和探戈……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(喂，亲爱的，别在跳舞的时候口嚼香糖!)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第三课:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多福饼，苹果布丁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"OneHundredandOneBestSongsCOh，Darling，YouTry，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安秀丽丹的迷人的‘唔’腔?)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男的要作洋奴T，V，宋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女的想学妖怪Madame蒋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"罗勃泰勒，克拉克蓋博，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是梦里的情郎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伊漱蕙蓬丝，玛丽蒙丹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是崇拜的偶像。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"安妮泰陈Figure生得最好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁顶Smart?约翰张!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说是，这样的才子佳人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才是户对门当。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黛维丝扬从不上国文课，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为老夫子的行头忒贼腔；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路易士赵打开中国地图，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"竟把洞庭湖看作鄱阳；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只知道美国有蜜丝佛陀香纷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不晓得东北有大豆高粱；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弄不清祖国的历史不打紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"话里不夹两句英文可不漂亮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据说:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“宁为美国狗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不作中国人。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是绅士淑女们的理想。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘记祖先，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忘记家乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是高等华人的风尚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，亲爱的蕙丽娜沈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有乔治吴和约翰张!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请问:“这到底是一种什么思想?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这到底是一种什么思想?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这到底是一种什么思想?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全中国人民知道一一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义曾经在中国"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"设立了多少爿奴才制造厂:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱伦，安娜，黛维丝……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是它画图打样；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"约翰，汤姆，罗勃特……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是它派工遣匠；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乔治，桃乐赛，惠灵顿……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是它精心培养。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一批比一批‘出色’，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一批比一批‘精良’；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一批比一批神经错乱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一批比一批丧心病狂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，亲爱的蕙丽娜沈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乔治吴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"约翰张，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁还有这些奴才思想?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清醒一下头脑吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能够再‘莫名其妙’!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经被狼咬伤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还硬说它不是狼?!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要知道:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天做一个中国人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气概多轩昂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举五星红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走在二十世纪历史的最前端!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五一、三、十。"}]}